metadata.name: Yaypngs #1
metadata.description: Yaypngs •• is an art driven community and growing IP. Our mission is to publish art that can be enjoyed by everyone for years to come. Yaypngs is an ode to the web3 space, NFT traders, and enthusiasts alike as we pay homage to the main file type we all have grown to love and trade. Each Yaypng comes filled with a variety of traits so you'll essentially find yourself as you've done many times with pngs.
